The paper deals with differential decoding schemes for multi-user MIMO systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and communications (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communications (cs.COM). The focus on MIMO systems and orthogonal space-time block codes also suggests a strong likelihood of the paper belonging to cs.IT and cs.NI.
